            "body": "I did some ready function in https://github.com/mhsjlw/flying-squid/blob/master/test/mineflayer.js , some of them can probably move to mineflayer. (for example onGround, waitMessage and waitSpawnZone)\r\n\r\nThe general idea here is there is no \"everything is ready\". There can only be \"X is ready\", \"Y is ready\",..\r\n\r\nAnd it's not only when the bot joins, stuff can get \"unready\" and then ready again (say if you are falling for example, you might want to know when you are on the ground  again)",
